product_name: Linksys AC1200 Dual Band WiFi 5 Router with Easy Setup Black
long_description:
Linksys Dual Band WiFi 5 Router

EASY SETUP: Installation is fast and easy, No CD required
DUAL-BAND WIRELESS AC: The Linksys AC1200 Dual Band WiFi 5 Router provides two dedicated Wi-Fi bands, providing double the bandwidth of a single band router.
KEEP YOUR NETWORK SAFE: Featuring WPA2 encryption and an SPI firewall, the AC1200 Dual Band WiFi 5 Router uses advanced security technologies to help keep your network safely connected.
ETHERNET FOR FAST WIRED CONNECTIONS: Four Ethernet ports allow you to connect wired devices directly for Internet access as well as share data on external storage devices.
CUSTOMIZE AND MANAGE YOUR HOME WIFI

Guest Access: Generate a separate, password-protected WiFi network for up to 10 guests and easily share the password via text.
Parental Controls: Ensure a safe Internet experience for your kids. Reduce online distractions during homework, family or dinnertime. Restrict access to inappropriate or distracting content, control usage, and block specific devices from accessing the Internet.
About Belkin International
At Belkin International, we create products that help people realize the power of technology and make people's lives better, easier and more fulfilling. This has been Belkin's mission since our inception in 1983.
Today, Belkin International has three brands – Belkin, Linksys and WeMo – to enhance the technology that connects us to the people, activities and experiences we love. Belkin products are renowned for their simplicity and ease of use, while our Linksys brand helped make wireless connectivity mainstream around the globe. Our newest brand, WeMo, is the leader in delivering customizable smart home experiences. Its product platform empowers people to monitor, measure and manage their electronics, appliances and lighting at home and on-the-go.

product_name: Linksys AX2200 Dual Band Mesh WiFi 6 System 2 2 Gbps
long_description:
Linksys Atlas 6 AX2200 Dual-Band Intelligent Mesh WiFi 6 Router, 2 pack features:
Blazing-Fast WiFi Speeds: No more buffering and lag. The AX2200 delivers speeds of up to 2.2 Gbps, ensuring smooth streaming, online gaming, and browsing across all your devices.

The AX2200 works together with compatible Linksys mesh nodes and routers, allowing you to easily extend coverage, eliminating dead zones. Easy Setup: With the Linksys App, setting up your new mesh WiFi system is simple. In just a few steps, you'll have your network up and running and ready to go. 
Advanced Security Features: Safeguard your digital world with WPA3 encryption, the latest WiFi security protocol.

product_name: Linksys Hydra 6 Dual Band Mesh Wi Fi 6 Router AX3000
long_description:
Easy setup and Control- The Linksys App makes it simple to setup, and lets you access your network from anywhere, and view or prioritize which connected devices are using the most Wi-Fi.
Make the Most of Wi-Fi 6 Speed- Access to 160 MHz channels enables the true power of Wi-Fi 6 technology, delivering the fastest connection with everything you do. 
Power of Wi-Fi 6- Four-stream Wi-Fi with up to 574 + 2402 Mbps for ultra-fast wireless speeds.  
Use of Routing- OFDMA increases efficiency in high-density scenarios, delivering high-speed Wi-Fi to multiple devices simultaneously.   
Reduces Power Consumption- Wi-Fi 6 (802.11ax) allows devices to negotiate when and how often they will wake up to send or receive data, substantially improving battery life for mobile and IoT devices.  
The Future Looks Bright- Future-ready hardware with Intelligent Mesh™.

product_name: Smart Wall Plug YoLink 1 4 Mile World s Longest Range In Wall Outlet 15A Compatible Alexa Google Assistant IFTTT App Remote Timer Schedules Scene Aut
long_description:
World's Longest Wireless Range: Powered by LoRa technology, the long-range yet low-power system offers the industry’s longest receiving range in the market (1/4 mile). Our long-range coverage enables its use in areas challenging for most residential Wi-Fi systems, such as basements, outdoor porch/patio areas, sheds, free-standing garages, even remote outbuildings on your property.

Works With Alexa & Google Voice Assistants: Supercharge your YoLink system by adding the YoLink skill to Alexa or Google Assistant. Control your YoLink devices by voice command (“Alexa, turn off the fan” – “OK!”) and control your YoLink devices as part of routines/automations that may include other, third-party, smart devices integrated with Alexa/Google.

Simple & Easy! YoLink’s Scan & Play smartphone app feature will have your smart plug up & ready in just a couple minutes! And the Wall Plug could not be easier to install: just add it to the app, and plug it into an available 120V receptacle. Done! Enjoy the convenience and energy bill savings of your new smart plug.

Set it & Forget it: Tired of forgetting to turn something off, or worried about leaving an iron or space heater on, or are there appliances/devices that you regularly turn off/on but wish it was automatic? Now, use the YoLink app to schedule automations, to automatically turn the power on or off at the time of your choice, on the days of the week of your choice.

YoLink Hub Required but not included: YoLink Hub is the only central controller for YoLink devices, and it connects YoLink devices into the internet and the cloud. Without YoLink Hub, YoLink smart power strip does not work with YoLink app and does not support 3rd-party integration with Alexa, Google Home and IFTTT.
The YoLink Smart Wall Plug sets the standard for smart home automation, offering an incredible 1/4 mile range that ensures reliable connectivity to your devices, no matter where you are on your property. Our innovative smart in-wall outlet is designed to handle up to 15A of power, making it the perfect solution for a wide range of devices, including lamps, fans, and small appliances.

Experience the convenience of the easy-to-use app, allowing you to customize your settings and receive real-time alerts directly to your smartphone. Seamlessly integrate the YoLink Smart Wall Plug with Alexa, Google Assistant, and IFTTT, enabling convenient voice commands and custom automations tailored to your unique needs.

Our versatile smart in-wall outlet is perfect for controlling any device you want to add to your smart home automation system, with the convenience of remote control, timer schedules, scene automation, and custom controls. Whether you're at home or away, you can always stay connected and in control.

Stay informed and in control with real-time app notifications, ensuring you're always aware of the status of your smart home devices. The YoLink Smart Wall Plug is the perfect addition to any smart home ecosystem, offering unparalleled range, versatility, and convenience.

Upgrade your smart home automation experience with the YoLink Smart Wall Plug, and discover the perfect combination of range, performance, and control. Transform your home into a fully automated smart home, and embrace the YoLink difference today!

Full APP Control: Manage access, create temporary or permanent codes, and control the lock from your smartphone. Ideal for Airbnb, vacation rentals, and porch watch.
Real-Time Notification & Alerts: Stay informed with activity notifications and view lock event history on the Revolo app. Auto-Lock function ensures your home is always secure.
Privacy Mode: Activate privacy function to disable password and app unlocking. Mechanical key or door knob are the only ways to unlock in this mode.

16A Max Load: With a maximum load capacity of 16A, this WiFi plug can handle high-powered devices such as air conditioners, heaters, and other appliances without any issues.
Real Timer: The S26 R2 WiFi Smart Plug comes with a built-in real-time timer function that allows you to set schedules for your devices. You can easily create a daily or weekly schedule to automate your devices according to your preferences.
Easy Installation and Setup: Setting up the S26 R2 WiFi Smart Plug is quick and simple. Just download the compatible app, connect the plug to your WiFi network, and you're ready to start controlling your devices. No hub or additional hardware required.
Smart Socket: This smart socket is compatible with voice assistants. You can control your devices with just your voice commands, making your life even more convenient and hands-free.

long_description:
Feature：
[Outdoor Smart Plug] With Outdoor Wi-Fi Plug, you can control lights, pumps and other devices using your smart phone anywhere and anytime. Turn on the Holiday Lights or schedule sprinklers without even going outside.
[No Hub Required] This outdoor plug works with your home Wi-Fi - no hub required. Just download the app, turn the smart jack on or off and plug it in. It also works with Alexa, Google Assistant.
[Compatibility] Outdoor Smart Weatherproof Plug is only compatible with 2.4GHz Wi-Fi networks. When sockets are not in use, they should remain closed with a waterproof cover.
[Control from anywhere] Using your home Wi-Fi, turn your seasonal lights on or off remotely from anywhere. Give your smart output a unique name for precise control. Ask your voice assistant to turn on the stereo and start the evening work in the pool.
[Unmatched Features] Compact design makes it easy to install. Features such as silicone cover, dust and harsh weather protection and general access, smart outdoor plug makes controlling your outdoor spaces more convenient.
[Remote Control App] With your smartphone or tablet, remotely control your wifi smart plug with the free smart Life or TuyaSmart App from anywhere anytime. Easy to manage home appliances.
[Information Sharing and Group Control] One tap to share a smart plug with your family member via the app to eliminate additional setup processes.
[Smart Script] Create your own scene to turn on/off household appliances in travel mode, home mode, temperature, humidity or other conditions.
